David Choe is an American painter, muralist, graffiti artist and graphic novelist from Los Angeles, CA. To learn more about him and his work check out the documentary "Dirty Hands: The Art and Crimes of David Choe" and also on his VICE series "Thumbs UP!"
Yoshi Obayashi is a stand-up comedian and host of his own podcast, Yoshi Didn't.

items.title: #316 - Enson Inoue, Chuck Liddell
items.content:encoded:
Enson Inoue is a Japanese-American mixed martial artist. He currently runs multiple training gyms throughout the world, and more recently traveled to northeast Japan to directly help the earthquake and tsunami victims in areas such as Fukushima.Chuck Lidell is an American mixed martial artist, and  former UFC Light Heavyweight Champion.
